<style>
  /* ============================================================
     BROADSHEET — strict black-on-white grid, hairline borders.
     The morning-of paper rundown for things too consequential.
     ============================================================ */

  :root {
    --black: #000;
    --white: #fff;
    --muted: #666;
    --hair: 1px solid #000;
  }

  *,
  *::before,
  *::after {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  html,
  body {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--black);
    font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .layout {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-left: var(--hair);
    border-right: var(--hair);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* === NAV === */
  .nav {
    display: flex;
    border-bottom: var(--hair);
  }
  .nav-cell {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    border-right: var(--hair);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .nav-cell:last-child {
    border-right: none;
  }
  .nav-cell.brand {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .nav-cell:hover {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .nav-cell.spacer {
    flex: 1;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .nav-cell.spacer:hover {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--black);
  }

  /* === BREADCRUMB === */
  .crumb {
    display: flex;
    border-bottom: var(--hair);
  }
  .crumb-cell {
    padding: 0.55rem 1.25rem;
    border-right: var(--hair);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .crumb-cell a {
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .crumb-cell a:hover {
    color: var(--black);
  }
  .crumb-cell:last-child {
    border-right: none;
    color: var(--black);
  }

  /* === HERO === */
  .hero-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr 240px;
    border-bottom: var(--hair);
  }
  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .hero-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  .hero-side {
    padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    border-right: var(--hair);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--muted);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .hero-side:last-child {
    border-right: none;
    border-left: var(--hair);
  }
  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .hero-side {
      border-right: none;
      border-left: none;
      border-bottom: var(--hair);
    }
    .hero-side:last-child {
      border-left: none;
    }
  }
  .hero-side .stat-num {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--black);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .hero-side .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.55rem;
  }
  .hero-center {
    padding: 3.5rem 2rem 3rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .giant-outline {
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--black);
    color: transparent;
    line-height: 0.92;
  }
  .giant-solid {
    -webkit-text-stroke: 0;
    color: var(--black);
    display: block;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 720px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--black);
  }

  /* === SECTION LABEL (filled) === */
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    border-bottom: var(--hair);
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .section-label .meta {
    color: var(--white);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  /* === STATS BAR === */
  .stats-bar {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    border-bottom: var(--hair);
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .stats-bar {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
  .stat-cell {
    padding: 1.25rem 1.25rem;
    border-right: var(--hair);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }
  .stat-cell:last-child {
    border-right: none;
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .stat-cell {
      border-bottom: var(--hair);
    }
    .stat-cell:nth-child(2n) {
      border-right: none;
    }
  }
  .stat-cell .k {
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .stat-cell .v {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  /* === APPS TABLE === */
  .apps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    border-bottom: var(--hair);
  }
  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .apps-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  .app {
    padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    border-right: var(--hair);
    border-bottom: var(--hair);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    background: var(--white);
    transition: background 0.12s;
  }
  .app:nth-child(2n) {
    border-right: none;
  }
  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .app {
      border-right: none;
    }
  }
  .app:hover {
    background: #f5f5f5;
  }
  .app .app-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    border-bottom: var(--hair);
    padding-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .app .num {
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .app .status-tag {
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border: var(--hair);
  }
  .app--pending .status-tag {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--black);
  }
  .app--live .status-tag {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .app .title {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .app .tagline {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    border-top: 1px dashed #000;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed #000;
    padding: 0.4rem 0;
  }
  .app .desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--black);
    line-height: 1.55;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .app .shot {
    display: block;
    border: var(--hair);
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--white);
  }
  .app .shot img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    filter: grayscale(1) contrast(1.05);
  }
  .app .ascii-frame {
    font-family: "Courier New", ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: 0;
    white-space: pre;
    padding: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 100%;
  }
  .app .ctas {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    border: var(--hair);
  }
  .app .btn {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.65rem 0.5rem;
    background: var(--white);
    border-right: var(--hair);
    color: var(--black);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.12s;
  }
  .app .btn:last-child {
    border-right: none;
  }
  .app .btn:hover {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .app .btn--single {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    border-right: none;
  }
  .app .prompt-link {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: right;
  }
  .app .prompt-link:hover {
    color: var(--black);
  }

  /* === EPILOGUE === */
  .epilogue {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: var(--hair);
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .epilogue {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  .epilogue-cell {
    padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    border-right: var(--hair);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .epilogue-cell:last-child {
    border-right: none;
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .epilogue-cell {
      border-right: none;
      border-bottom: var(--hair);
    }
    .epilogue-cell:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
  }
  .epilogue-cell .e-label {
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* === FOOTER === */
  .term-footer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
</style>

<main class="layout">
  <nav class="nav">
    <a class="nav-cell brand" href="https://links.vibes.diy/homepage">VIBES.DIY</a>
    <a class="nav-cell" href="/expressions/">Expressions</a>
    <span class="nav-cell spacer"></span>
    <a class="nav-cell" href="https://links.vibes.diy/discord">Discord</a>
    <a class="nav-cell" href="https://links.vibes.diy/CLI">CLI</a>
  </nav>

  <div class="crumb">
    <span class="crumb-cell"><a href="/">Home</a></span>
    <span class="crumb-cell"><a href="/expressions/">Expressions</a></span>
    <span class="crumb-cell">Day-of Run-of-Show</span>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-row">
    <aside class="hero-side">
      <div>
        <div>Cluster</div>
        <div class="stat-num" style="margin-top: .35rem;">06</div>
        <div class="stat-label">/ ten clusters</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div>Source</div>
        <div class="stat-label" style="font-size:.7rem; letter-spacing:.05em; color:#000;">tilted-enterprise-tail</div>
        <div class="stat-label">entries 51–60</div>
      </div>
    </aside>
    <div class="hero-center">
      <h1 class="giant-outline">Day-of<br /><span class="giant-solid">Run-of-Show</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">All-hands cue sheets, IPO roadshow choreography, layoff-day
        timing, board rundowns. The morning-of app for things too
        consequential for a Sheet — time horizon: hours; stakes:
        career-visible.</p>
    </div>
    <aside class="hero-side">
      <div>
        <div>Apps</div>
        <div class="stat-num" style="margin-top: .35rem;">10</div>
        <div class="stat-label">/ in this rundown</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div>Skin</div>
        <div class="stat-label" style="font-size:.7rem; letter-spacing:.05em; color:#000;">Broadsheet</div>
        <div class="stat-label">strict b/w grid</div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>

  <div class="section-label">
    <span>The Rundown</span>
    <span class="meta">10 apps · 06 / 10 clusters</span>
  </div>

  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <span class="k">Persistence</span>
      <span class="v">Fireproof</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <span class="k">Time Horizon</span>
      <span class="v">Hours</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <span class="k">Stakes</span>
      <span class="v">High</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <span class="k">Buyer</span>
      <span class="v">Team Lead</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="apps-grid">
    {{#each apps}}
      <article class="app {{#if live}}app--live{{else}}app--pending{{/if}}">
        <div class="app-head">
          <span class="num">No. {{num}} · {{slug}}</span>
          {{#if live}}
            <span class="status-tag">Live</span>
          {{else}}
            <span class="status-tag">Pending</span>
          {{/if}}
        </div>
        <h2 class="title">{{title}}</h2>
        <p class="tagline">{{tagline}}</p>
        <p class="desc">{{desc}}</p>
        {{#if live}}
          <a
            class="shot"
            href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}"
            aria-label="{{title}} screenshot"
          >
            <img
              src="https://{{slug}}--{{author}}.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg"
              alt="{{slug}}"
              onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='{{@root.assetPrefix}}images/og-preview.png';"
            />
          </a>
          <div class="ctas">
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Join</a>
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}?skipChat=true">Clone</a>
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Remix</a>
          </div>
          <a
            class="prompt-link"
            href="https://vibes.diy/chat/prompt?prompt64={{prompt64 desc}}"
          >› Start Fresh from this prompt</a>
        {{else}}
          <div class="shot">
            <pre class="ascii-frame">+----------------------+
|                      |
|   awaiting deploy    |
|                      |
+----------------------+</pre>
          </div>
          <div class="ctas">
            <a
              class="btn btn--single"
              href="https://vibes.diy/chat/prompt?prompt64={{prompt64 desc}}"
            >Start From This Prompt</a>
          </div>
        {{/if}}
      </article>
    {{/each}}
  </section>

  <div class="section-label">
    <span>Endnotes</span>
    <span class="meta">read me · hack</span>
  </div>

  <div class="epilogue">
    <div class="epilogue-cell">
      <div class="e-label">READ ME</div>
      <p>Ten takes on the same shape — a workflow that lives or dies on the
        morning of the event, when the rundown lives in a Sheet that nobody
        trusts. Replaces shared Sheets, paper rundowns, and "did we cue the
        slides?" panic. Time horizon: hours. Stakes: career-visible.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="epilogue-cell">
      <div class="e-label">HACK</div>
      <p>Hit
        <a
          href="https://vibes.diy/remix/og/ipo-roadshow?skipChat=true"
          style="text-decoration: underline;"
        >Clone</a>
        on any rundown to spin up your own copy, or
        <a
          href="https://vibes.diy/remix/og/ipo-roadshow"
          style="text-decoration: underline;"
        >Remix</a>
        to ask the model to reshape the code. Pending entries link straight to
        the prompt that built them.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  {{> newsletter}}
<footer class="term-footer">
    <span>Vibes.diy
      ·
      <a href="https://links.vibes.diy/homepage" style="text-decoration: underline;">homepage</a>
      ·
      <a href="/expressions/" style="text-decoration: underline;">expressions</a></span>
    <span>End of rundown</span>
  </footer>
</main>
